            "id": 1,
            "parent": 3,
            "text": "Cases of COVID-19 are escalating rapidly across the globe ,",
            "relation": "BACKGROUND"
        },
        {
            "id": 2,
            "parent": 1,
            "text": "with the mortality risk being especially high among those with existing illness and multimorbidity . <S>",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 3,
            "parent": 0,
            "text": "This study aimed to synthesise evidence for the role and response of palliative care and hospice teams to viral epi / pandemics ,",
            "relation": "ROOT"
        },
        {
            "id": 4,
            "parent": 3,
            "text": "to inform the COVID-19 pandemic response . <S> <P>",
            "relation": "ENABLEMENT"
        },
        {
            "id": 5,
            "parent": 3,
            "text": "We conducted a rapid systematic review according to PRISMA guidelines in five databases . <S>",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 6,
            "parent": 5,
            "text": "Of 3094 papers identified , ten were included in this narrative synthesis . <S> <P>",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 7,
            "parent": 6,
            "text": "Included studies were from West Africa , Taiwan , Hong Kong , Singapore , the United States and Italy . <S>",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 8,
            "parent": 6,
            "text": "All had an observational design . <S>",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 9,
            "parent": 3,
            "text": "Findings were synthesised",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 10,
            "parent": 9,
            "text": "using a previously proposed framework",
            "relation": "MANNER-MEANS"
        },
        {
            "id": 11,
            "parent": 9,
            "text": "according to ' systems '",
            "relation": "SAME-UNIT"
        },
        {
            "id": 12,
            "parent": 11,
            "text": "( policies , training and protocols , communication and coordination , data ) ,",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
