            "text": "( community provision , use of technology )",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 17,
            "parent": 15,
            "text": "and ' stuff '",
            "relation": "SAME-UNIT"
        },
        {
            "id": 18,
            "parent": 17,
            "text": "( medicines and equipment , personal protective equipment ) . <S>",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 19,
            "parent": 20,
            "text": "We conclude",
            "relation": "ATTRIBUTION"
        },
        {
            "id": 20,
            "parent": 3,
            "text": "that hospice and palliative services have an essential role in the response to COVID-19 by :",
            "relation": "FINDINGS"
        },
        {
            "id": 21,
            "parent": 20,
            "text": "1 ) responding rapidly and flexibly ;",
            "relation": "MANNER-MEANS"
        },
        {
            "id": 22,
            "parent": 21,
            "text": "2 ) ensuring protocols for symptom management are available ,",
            "relation": "JOINT"
        },
        {
            "id": 23,
            "parent": 22,
            "text": "and training non - specialists in their use ;",
            "relation": "JOINT"
        },
        {
            "id": 24,
            "parent": 21,
            "text": "3 ) being involved in triage ;",
            "relation": "JOINT"
        },
        {
            "id": 25,
